on to the presence of two length scales,\nenergetic and entropic effects associated with local minima and curvatures of\nthe pair interaction play an important role in determining the presence of\nwater-like anomalies and the liquid-liquid phase transition.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 21 Mar 2011 19:15:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-27"}
